                            <comment id="14662606" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 7 Aug 2015 22:54:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user chenliang613 commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/972#issuecomment-128853048&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/972#issuecomment-128853048&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

